M|CSS |tx|}
M|CSS |tx|```
M|CSS |**Ex|**
M|CSS |tx|```tsx
M|CSS |func|{ messages: Message[] }) {
M|CSS |tx|return (
M|CSS |tx|<div className="overflow-y-auto h-screen">
M|CSS |tx|{messages.map(msg => (
M|CSS |tx|<div key={msg.id} className="message-item">
M|CSS |tx|<Avatar us={msg.author} />
M|CSS |tx|<div>{msg.cn}</div>
M|CSS |tx|</div>
M|CSS |tx|))}
M|CSS |tx|</div>
